#. Tag: screen
#: ay_bigfile.xml:9432
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&lt;general&gt;\n"
"  &lt;ask-list config:type=\"list\"&gt;\n"
"    &lt;ask&gt;\n"
"      &lt;script&gt;\n"
